James F. Kelly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_F._Kelly 0 James F. Kelly is an American actor best known for playing Robert F. Kennedy (whom Kelly closely resembles). Between the years 1981 and 1997 he played RFK in seven different productions. He also portrayed John F. Kennedy in the 1992 television miniseries Sinatra (TV miniseries).
